thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Louis Liew

author: Louis Liew
title: Louis Liew
text: Walked in the Canninton store for the first time and bought a pair of headphones through a friend's recommendation. The service was great, staff was very helpful and knowledgeable. Will definitely go back there to get more things in the future. And they also do price matching on anything you wanted to get.
